Tuto:

git clone git@github.com:dam1/Image-Service-Api-Example---Node-Js.git

cf push cloudimageapi --no-manifest  -b git://github.com/dam1/cloudfoundry-custom.git

"-b git://github.com/da..." let us choose a custom buildpacks

